    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You should change </p>\n\n<pre><code>BigInteger toHex=new BigInteger(dec,16);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>to</p>\n\n<pre><code>BigInteger toHex=new BigInteger(dec,10);\n                                     ^\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Currently you ask the user for a dec-value, and then interpret the input as a hex-value. (That's why the output is identical to the input.)</p>\n"
